e.\r\n\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_7196\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7196\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7196 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014250\/reading-chairs-online-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Reading chairs online where bedroom is equipped with a beautiful dark purple armchair to get some reading done\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014250\/reading-chairs-online-for-your-home.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014250\/reading-chairs-online-for-your-home-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014250\/reading-chairs-online-for-your-home-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014250\/reading-chairs-online-for-your-home-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7196\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">A dark lilac leather armchair next to a beautiful window in a high ceiling bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<h2>Snuggle Up Lazy Bug! There&#8217;s Is Chair By Your Side<\/h2>\r\nHave you had a chairgasm yet? You heard it right, a chairgasm is that feeling of euphoria you experience when you rest in your chair. Those of you who love to snuggle up in your chairs with a Harry Potter book in your hand this brown armchair with cushions resembling the colour of coffee is a must-have. For more comfort, you can place this comfy reading chair close to your bed, so you can pop your legs right up and relax.\r\n\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_7195\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7195\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7195 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014245\/reading-chair-for-your-home-with-brown-armchair.jpg\" alt=\"Reading chair for your home with brown armchair with cushions resembling the colour of coffee\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014245\/reading-chair-for-your-home-with-brown-armchair.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014245\/reading-chair-for-your-home-with-brown-armchair-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014245\/reading-chair-for-your-home-with-brown-armchair-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014245\/reading-chair-for-your-home-with-brown-armchair-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7195\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">A snuggly coffee cushioned reading chair is perfect to slink into after a long day<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do you want a free design consultation, call our designers\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28125622\/do-you-want-free-design-consultation.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\r\n<h2>Munch, Sip, Read! You Have The Best Reading Chair<\/h2>\r\nKeep your books close, but your snacks even closer. This is honestly the best reading chair ever created. Look at it! If you are a lazy bum, this chair is your dream come true. This reading chair comes with an inbuilt mini shelf at the arm of the chair, and the armrest is like a mini countertop! Bliss much, you can now enjoy your munching and sipping on some tea while reading. Who wouldn\u2019t want to invest in a reading chair like this!\r\n\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_7197\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7197\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7197 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014254\/reading-table-and-chair-with-inbuilt-mini-shelf.jpg\" alt=\"Reading table and chair with inbuilt mini shelf at the arm of the chair and you can keep your books close\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014254\/reading-table-and-chair-with-inbuilt-mini-shelf.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014254\/reading-table-and-chair-with-inbuilt-mini-shelf-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014254\/reading-table-and-chair-with-inbuilt-mini-shelf-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014254\/reading-table-and-chair-with-inbuilt-mini-shelf-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7197\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">A unique reading share with an inbuilt bookshelf<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<h2>Double Trouble! With These Two Reading Chairs<\/h2>\r\nTwo empty chairs are not a good use of space, fill them up with love. Who said that reading chairs are meant to be used only while reading? Not us! So let\u2019s have some fun! Two chairs are always better than one. If you\u2019re the kind who just has one friend and lives to host tea parties, then these reading chairs are just apt. With wooden legs made of white velvet material, these reading chairs bring out a classy, elegant look.\r\n\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_7193\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7193\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7193 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014237\/comfortable-reading-chair-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Comfortable reading chair for your home with wooden legs made of white velvet material\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014237\/comfortable-reading-chair-for-your-home.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014237\/comfortable-reading-chair-for-your-home-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014237\/comfortable-reading-chair-for-your-home-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014237\/comfortable-reading-chair-for-your-home-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7193\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Beautifully designed twin white reading chairs with wooden legs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<h2>Where There&#8217;s A Chair There Should Be Table!<\/h2>\r\nYou all know that serious reading and writing cannot happen on the bed. We all have tried this technique and failed. We flop like jelly and flip into bed. But hey hold your horses with this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/study-room-interiors\/modern-study-table-designs\/\">study unit design<\/a> that has a reading table with a chair you can get the best of both, reading and writing. So if you have kids, this is definitely a smart investment. You would want your kid to cut down on zzz\u2019s and concentrate on the grades, right?\r\n\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_7198\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7198\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7198 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014258\/reading-table-with-chair-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Reading table with chair for your home where you can get the best of both, reading and writing\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014258\/reading-table-with-chair-for-your-home.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014258\/reading-table-with-chair-for-your-home-300x180.jpg 300w, htt